description: Everything about New York is fascinating, including its statistics. If you're curious, you can ask "What's the length of Manhattan?"  or "How many languages are spoken in New York?"  or "Who was the first European to see Manhattan".  There almost 100 New York facts in this version. Please, let me know what else you'd like Portable NYC to tell you.
